{"tha-ap470:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap470:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap470:0.3":"8 Pilakkhaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap470:1.1":"“Vanantare buddham disva, ","tha-ap470:1.2":"atthadassim mahayasam; ","tha-ap470:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap470:1.4":"pilakkhassa phalam ada. ","tha-ap470:2.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap470:2.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap470:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap470:2.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap470:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap470:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap470:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap470:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap470:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap470:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap470:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap470:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap470:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap470:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pilakkhaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap470:7.1":"Pilakkhaphaladayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}